before long.

79
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,359
But thank you very much.

80
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:43,754
Right, hold it there
while we check the tape.

81
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:46,559
- How did it go?
- Well, I thought... First class.

82
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:49,314
- Very good indeed.
- I thought I waffled a bit.

83
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:52,392
Oh no, you stonewalled
superbly, Minister.

84
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,629
Time fora drink?

85
